data.description: Introducing a remodeled Clovis home, conveniently located near Fresno State. This residence boasts an impressive 5 bedrooms and 3 baths, providing ample space for your growing family or hosting guests. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a long driveway that offers plenty of parking options for you and your visitors. Step inside and be captivated by the updated landscaping that beautifully frames the entrance. The interior has commercial-grade vinyl flooring. The crown molding adds an elegant touch, elevating the aesthetics of each room. With an open floor plan, this home effortlessly combines functionality and style. The seamless flow between the living spaces creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining family and friends. One of the features of this property is the converted garage, which was transformed into a versatile space with 2 additional bedrooms. This unique setup could be used as an in-law suite, offering a private and comfortable living area for extended family members or guests. Outside, a covered patio awaits. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remodeled Clovis home near Fresno State!
